Robert E. TURNER, Appellant, v. Alfin YOUNG et al., Appellees. No. 25857. United States Court of Appeals Fifth Circuit. Nov. 4, 1968. Rehearing Denied Dec. 13, 1968. Robert E. Turner, Lake Charles, La., for appellant. Meredith T. Holt, Nathan A. Cormie, Cormie & Morgan, Lake Charles, La., for appellees.

Before DYER and SIMPSON, Circuit Judges, and CABOT, District Judge.

PER CURIAM:

The judgment of the District Court is in all respects

Affirmed.
